    <title>Enforce domain ownership</title>
    <para>
        Policies should be owned by policies, clients, by client relationship management, accounts by finance and so on.
        Only the owners should modify their own domain objects, and should provide <emphasis>controlled</emphasis> access to user information
        to its users via services.
    </para>
